Payment,Savvy,is,a,payment,processing,provider,that,offers,ACH,credit,card,support,and,online,payment,gateway,Additionally,it,supports,chargeback,protection,recurring,billing,and,pay,by,texting,The,Payment,Savvy,API,integrates,this,platform,with,third,party,applications,and,offers,low,rates,and,free,payment,processing,using,a,convenience,fee,model